# Performance & media

Full checklist: `docs/static-site-standards.md` (Performance, Images/media).

## Targets

- Lighthouse 100% aspirational; optimize LCP, INP, CLS

## Critical path

- Inline critical CSS for above-the-fold; defer non-critical CSS
- `<link rel="preload">` for LCP image/font; `preconnect` / `dns-prefetch` for third parties (fonts, CDN)
- Scripts: `defer` modules; no render-blocking JS; minimal payload

## Images & video

- `<picture>`: AVIF → WebP → fallback; `srcset` + `sizes`
- `loading="lazy"`, `decoding="async"`, `fetchpriority="high"` on LCP image only
- Always set `width` and `height` (or aspect-ratio) to prevent CLS
- Compress assets (Squoosh / ImageOptim); prefer inline SVG for icons/logos
- Video: `poster`, `preload="none"` unless autoplay required

## Fonts

- Max 2 families; subset weights; preload critical woff2; see fonts-icons rule

## Infra

- HTTP/2+ via Cloudflare (deployment concern — do not block HTML on heavy third parties)
